answers.answer: Pains under right rib cages are usually liver problems

question: My husband has Type 2 diabetes. For the last two months he has been having a needle like pain in his back on both sides under rib cage.It is not there all the time but does anyone know what that is.He said it is very annoying.Sometimes it moves to the front right side.
title: Prickling pain in back under rib cage
